                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <span class="year">2022</span>
                        <a href="https://theoffingmag.com/interviews/qa-with-niina-pollari-and-grzegorz-kwiatkowski/">Conversation with Grzegorz Kwiatkowski</a> 
                        <span class="venue">The Offing</span>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <span class="year">2022</span>
                        <a href="https://www.triangle.house/blog/pollari-x-fletcher">Conversation with Sasha Fletcher</a> 
                        <span class="venue">Triangle House</span>
