            </div>

            <div class="writing-section">
                <h3>Podcasts & Audio</h3>
                <ul class="writing-list">
                    <li>
                        <span class="year">2024</span>
                        <a href="https://www.slowdownshow.org/episode/2024/06/26/1148-urine-season-by-niina-pollari">The Slowdown, Episode 1148</a>
                        <p class="description-text">Leslie Sainz discusses my poem "Urine Season" on the poetry podcast The Slowdown</p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <span class="year">2023</span>
                        <a href="https://eriddifordgraham.substack.com/p/episode-10-niina-pollari-on-truths">Multi-Verse, Episode 10: “Truth's Heart of Stone”</a>
