                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <span class="year">2022</span>
                        <a href="Poetry Off the Shelf (2022)">Poetry Off the Shelf</a>
                        <p class="description-text">Discussing Path of Totality with Helena de Groot on the Poetry Foundation podcast.</p>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>

        </div>
    </section>
</MainLayout>

<style>
    .writing-container {
        margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    .writing-section {
        margin-bottom: 4rem;
    }

    .writing-section h3 {
        font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 2px;
        color: #999;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
        padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .writing-list {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
    }

    .writing-list li {
        margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
        line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .year {
        font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        color: #bbb;
        display: inline-block;
        width: 45px;
    }

    .writing-list a {
        color: #1a1a1a;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-bottom: 1px solid transparent;
        transition: border-color 0.2s;
    }

    .writing-list a:hover {
        border-bottom: 1px solid #1a1a1a;
    }

    .venue {
        font-style: italic;
        color: #666;
        margin-left: 0.5rem;
    }

    .description-text {
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        color: #555;
        margin: 0.5rem 0 0 45px;
        font-style: italic;
    }
</style>